# Tabs

<p class=""description"">Tabs make it easy to explore and switch between different views.</p>

[Tabs](https://material.io/design/components/tabs.html) organize and allow navigation between groups of content that are related and at the same level of hierarchy.

## Installing with Nuget

You can [install Tab package](https://www.nuget.org/packages/Skclusive.Material.Tab/) by typing the below command in your terminal:

`dotnet add package Skclusive.Material.Tab`

Then, you can import it in your _Imports.razor.

```csharp
@using Skclusive.Material.Tab;
```

